Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:31.69,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我常常不以为然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:34.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不能让人知晓的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:38.72,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}隐瞒着一路走来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:42.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}这份无边漫延的苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:45.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就由我一人全部承受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:49.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}那些终将消逝的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:53.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我一概不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:58.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}希望自己变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.49,0:23:01.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我许下这样的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:04.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}仿佛那冲破黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.18,0:23:08.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}孤独的晨星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:12.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}深深沉沦的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:15.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}脆弱不堪的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:19.37,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}溢于言表
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:22.83,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不言而喻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:28.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}唯有隐姓埋名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:32.83,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}静候曙光来临
